    <p>Stay­ing cosy and com­fort­able in the pan­demic cer­tainly brought forth a re­nais­sance of the cardi­gan last year. But, in­stead of im­prac­ti­cal chunky knits, in­flu­encers and celebri­ties opted for svelte, cropped op­tions to do dou­ble duty by also show­ing off their fig­ures.</p>
    <p>Wear it as a top fully but­toned up or over a match­ing cami, and you have a pre­sentable out­fit to go from Zoom call to quick er­rand in town.</p>


